s:70:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/website-transformations-start-tonight.htm\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/website-transformations-start-tonight.htm#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 30 Sep 2013 14:53:12 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/?p=18872\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:536:\"<p>A reminder that we are going to transform a whole lot of websites this week as part of WP Academy&#8217;s free &#34;WordPress Mechanic&#34; series. Tonight at 7pm EST, I am going to take an amateur website (my ex-wife&#8217;s and show you exactly what I am doing to turn it into a site that you might [&#8230;]</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/website-transformations-start-tonight.htm\">Website Transformations start tonight</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com\">WordPress Training</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"marc\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1773:\"<p></p><p><strong>A reminder that we are going to transform a whole lot of websites this week as part of WP Academy&#8217;s free &quot;WordPress Mechanic&quot; series.</strong></p>  <p>Tonight at 7pm EST, I am going to take an amateur website (my ex-wife&#8217;s <img src=\'http://members.wpacademy.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_wink.gif\' alt=\';)\' class=\'wp-smiley\' />  and show you exactly what I am doing to turn it into a site that you might have paid $3000 for.&#160; I will show you how <u>you</u> can do this too for a tiny fraction of that price.&#160; Then George will come in with his favorite plugins and more student case-studies.&#160; </p>  <p>Later in the week, you will have two more opportunities to get direct one-on-one assistance from our expert instructors George and Pamela, and witness the type of work that happens every day with students of our <a href=\"http://wpacademy.com/wordpress-training\">WP Live course</a> (which begins next week, incidentally) </p>  <p>And oh, did I mention the price?&#160;&#160; You will like it <img src=\'http://members.wpacademy.com/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_wink.gif\' alt=\';)\' class=\'wp-smiley\' /> </p>  <p><em></em></p>  <p><em>Note: These sessions are recorded, but only for <a href=\"http://wpencyclopedia.com\">WP Encyclopedia subscribers</a>. </em> <em>If you are not a subscriber, you will need join one of the live sessions to benefit.&#160; </em></p>  <p>All Details in <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-coaching-and-website-improvement-next-week.htm\">Original post</a></p><p>The post <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/website-transformations-start-tonight.htm\">Website Transformations start tonight</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com\">WordPress Training</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/website-transformations-start-tonight.htm/feed\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:47:\"Free Coaching and Website Improvement next week\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:80:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-coaching-and-website-improvement-next-week.htm\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:89:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-coaching-and-website-improvement-next-week.htm#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 26 Sep 2013 17:35:51 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/?p=18864\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:606:\"<p>Three opportunities this week to upgrade your website and learn! Monday Sep. 30, 7pm EST Themes and Plugins (followed by live coaching and critiques), by WP Academy lead instructors Marc Beneteau and George Plumley &#62;&#62; Register HERE &#60;&#60; We are teaming-up to bring you: Best Themes Review, by Marc Beneteau Best Plugins Review, by George [&#8230;]</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-coaching-and-website-improvement-next-week.htm\">Free Coaching and Website Improvement next week</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com\">WordPress Training</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"marc\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2542:\"<p></p><p>Three opportunities this week to upgrade your website and learn!</p>  <h3>Monday Sep. 30, 7pm EST</h3>  <p><strong>Themes and Plugins (followed by live coaching and critiques),</strong> by WP Academy lead instructors Marc Beneteau and George Plumley</p>  <p><a href=\"https://www3.gotomeeting.com/register/113442958\"><strong>&gt;&gt; Register HERE &lt;&lt;</strong></a></p>  <p>We are teaming-up to bring you: </p>  <ul>   <li>Best Themes Review, by Marc Beneteau</li>    <li>Best Plugins Review, by George Plumley</li>    <li>Q&amp;A + Website improvement / coaching&#160; (20 min)</li>    <li>WP Live program presentation</li> </ul>  <p>You especially won’t want to miss George and I joining forces to focus on <em><strong>your</strong></em> website!</p>  <h3>Tuesday Oct. 1, 7pm EST</h3>  <p><strong>Open Coaching with George Plumley</strong>.&#160;&#160; </p>  <p>Take your website to the “WordPress Mechanic” and watch him while he works.&#160; Alternatively drill him with your questions.&#160; </p>  <p>Attend this session at our <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/public\">Public Coaching</a>.&#160; Pre-registration is not required, maximum attendance 25.</p>  <h3>Thursday Oct. 3, 2pm EST</h3>  <p><strong>Open Coaching with Pamela Bey, WP Academy instructor</strong></p>  <p>Pamela is our e-commerce specialist.&#160; </p>  <p>Attend this session at our <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/public\">Public Coaching</a>.&#160; Pre-registration is not required.</p>  <h3>What is “WP Live” ? </h3>  <p><a href=\"http://wpacademy.com/wordpress-training\">WP Live</a> is a unique education and coaching program on WordPress web design and web marketing.&#160; </p>  <p><strong>Our next WP Live starts on <u>Tuesday Oct. 8 at 7pm EST</u></strong> and <a href=\"http://wpacademy.com/wordpress-training\">Registration is Open</a>.&#160; Register early to gain additional weeks of support.</p>  <p>One of our graduates just wrote to me: </p>  <p><em>“I wanted to tell you that I think George is an incredible instructor. He is clear, humorous, and covers a whole lot of ground in each lecture.&#160; Thank you for providing this class – I am finally feeling empowered with wordpress</em>.” – Sue C., Manorville NY.</p>  <p>Please join us at one of the times above.&#160; </p><p>The post <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-coaching-and-website-improvement-next-week.htm\">Free Coaching and Website Improvement next week</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com\">WordPress Training</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:85:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-coaching-and-website-improvement-next-week.htm/feed\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"Website branding: amazing values from our partner, Christopher Staser\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:100:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/website-branding-amazing-values-from-our-partner-christopher-staser.htm\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:109:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/website-branding-amazing-values-from-our-partner-christopher-staser.htm#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 24 Sep 2013 14:42:59 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/?p=18852\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:714:\"<p>Last week we had Christopher Staser, branding expert and high-end WordPress developer present a webinar entitled Integrated Branding: The Look, the Language, the Story.&#160; The webinar summarizes his experience creating over 50 brands, and led to a lively discussion.&#160; Here is the free, non-expiring recording of that webinar: http://members.wpacademy.com/w9-branding In addition, Christopher has put together [&#8230;]</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/website-branding-amazing-values-from-our-partner-christopher-staser.htm\">Website branding: amazing values from our partner, Christopher Staser</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com\">WordPress Training</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"marc\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4201:\"<p></p><p>Last week we had Christopher Staser, branding expert and high-end WordPress developer present a webinar entitled<strong> Integrated Branding: The Look, the Language, the Story.</strong>&#160; The webinar summarizes his experience creating over 50 brands, and led to a lively discussion.&#160; Here is the free, non-expiring recording of that webinar: </p>  <p><a title=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/w9-branding\" href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/w9-branding\"><strong>http://members.wpacademy.com/w9-branding</strong></a></p>  <p>In addition, Christopher has put together a truly incredible offer on the webinar, exclusively for WP Academy subscribers. This is an opportunity that I am passing on to you at cost.&#160; Last time we shared this we made several very happy customers.</p>  <p><b>Complete business Rebrand + Logo + Website, for $3250.</b></p>  <p><b>He normally sells this package to his start-up clients for $10K.</b></p>  <p>If you need to :</p>  <ul>   <li>Clarify and perfect your brand, tagline and messaging including brand and domain naming</li>    <li>Give your website a $10k facelift (but you don’t have $10k to invest)</li>    <li>Redo your logo and visual styles and have them available for new marketing collateral</li> </ul>  <p>Then Christopher is your man.</p>  <p>Review his credentials at <a href=\"http://brandweaver.tv/\">http://brandweaver.tv</a></p>  <p><b>Here is what you get</b></p>  <p><b>Branding: Verbal Positioning and Messaging</b></p>  <ul>   <li>4-8 hour Discovery Session</li>    <li>Brand name review and naming—Christopher has named 45 companies</li>    <li>Key tagline and messaging</li>    <li>Core brand DNA and personality definition</li> </ul>  <p><b>Logo</b></p>  <ul>   <li>Logo that is in alignment with the brand DNA</li>    <li>Timeless design principles that will keep your logo strong for decades and across media</li> </ul>  <p><b>Website</b></p>  <ul>   <li>Awesome WordPress website in alignment your brand with strong visual expression and potent visual messaging</li>    <li>Full featured site with galleries, embedded media, blogs, shopping carts, etc.</li>    <li>Integrated SEO, social media and web marketing considerations</li> </ul>  <p>Consider that this includes his 4-8 hour brand discovery session called the Discovery Dig – something at which Christopher is a genius and has pioneered his unique approach in the industry. He normally charges $2500/day just for this.&#160; As a happy customer myself, I can say that this alone (Discovery Dig) paid for his services.</p>  <p><b>What’s the catch?</b></p>  <p>No catch.&#160; It’s just that Christopher can only offer two of these deeply discounted packages the rest of this year.&#160; He is asking serious clients to write or call him directly (<a href=\"mailto:chris@brandweaver.tv\">chris@brandweaver.tv</a>, <u>801-448-6319</u>)&#160; to see if there is a fit. He will evaluate your current brand, logo and website when you speak. </p>  <p><em>To lock-in this price, he is requesting that the deal be closed and a 50% deposit paid by Friday, September 27, and the project to be completed over 12 weeks.</em></p>  <p><b>What if you don&#8217;t have the budget or want to build it yourself?</b></p>  <p>Christopher also offered a <em>Website Brand Diagnosis</em>. This is a 30-45 minute call where he&#8217;ll &quot;download&quot; his insights into your current website and brand including:</p>  <ul>   <li>Name/messaging evaluation</li>    <li>Logo evaluation and suggestions</li>    <li>Story/culture evaluation</li>    <li>Sales, social media evaluation and suggestions</li> </ul>  <p>This is normally $150, but he is offering it at $75 through Friday 9/27: <a href=\"http://brandweaver.tv/services/website-brand-diagnosis\">http://brandweaver.tv/services/website-brand-diagnosis</a></p>  <p>Cheers,</p>  <p>Marc Beneteau   <br />”Your Small-Biz Web Technology Mentor” </p><p>The post <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/website-branding-amazing-values-from-our-partner-christopher-staser.htm\">Website branding: amazing values from our partner, Christopher Staser</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com\">WordPress Training</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:105:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/website-branding-amazing-values-from-our-partner-christopher-staser.htm/feed\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:84:\"Integrated Website Branding: The look, the language, the story (Free Class Thursday)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:112:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/integrated-website-branding-the-look-the-language-the-story-free-class-thursday.htm\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:121:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/integrated-website-branding-the-look-the-language-the-story-free-class-thursday.htm#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 17 Sep 2013 14:01:30 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/?p=18827\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:666:\"<p>We are excited and honored to host Branding expert and WordPress developer Christopher Staser again, this coming Thursday 9/19, 7pm EST.&#160; Our previous session was very popular and led to a lively audience chat – so we booked him again to share his secrets in redesigning over 45 brands (including the WP Academy website!) You&#8217;ll [&#8230;]</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/integrated-website-branding-the-look-the-language-the-story-free-class-thursday.htm\">Integrated Website Branding: The look, the language, the story (Free Class Thursday)</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com\">WordPress Training</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"marc\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2047:\"<p></p><p><img title=\"christopher-staser\" style=\"float: right; display: inline\" alt=\"\" align=\"right\" src=\"http://wpacademy.tv/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/christopher-staser.jpg\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" />We are excited and honored to host <strong>Branding expert and WordPress developer Christopher Staser again, this coming <u>Thursday 9/19, 7pm EST</u></strong>.&#160; Our previous session was very popular and led to a lively audience chat – so we booked him again to share his secrets in redesigning over 45 brands (including the WP Academy website!)</p>  <ul>   <li>You&#8217;ll learn the principles he uses on each project to discover and then express the brand&#8217;s unique and authentic voice </li>    <li>You&#8217;ll see a half-dozen examples of brand transformation that will inspire your own project </li>    <li>You&#8217;ll discover the questions to ask yourself to begin your own branding journey – getting this down will give you a quantum leap in credibility and sales </li>    <li>As a bonus, Christopher will be diagnosing two attendees sites live and there will be a drawing for a free 30 minute web-brand evaluation worth $150 </li> </ul>  <p>Christopher is the founder of <a href=\"http://brandweaver.tv\">BrandWeaver</a>.&#160; He has won several national awards in film, video and photography. He stands out as a brand designer for his unique combination of abilities as a brand strategist, visual designer and writer-storyteller.</p>  <p>Register for the live webinar <u>Thursday, September 19 at 7pm</u> EST here: </p>  <p><a title=\"https://www3.gotomeeting.com/register/205191830\" href=\"https://www3.gotomeeting.com/register/205191830\"><strong>https://www3.gotomeeting.com/register/205191830</strong></a></p><p>The post <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/integrated-website-branding-the-look-the-language-the-story-free-class-thursday.htm\">Integrated Website Branding: The look, the language, the story (Free Class Thursday)</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com\">WordPress Training</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:117:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/integrated-website-branding-the-look-the-language-the-story-free-class-thursday.htm/feed\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"Entrepreneur mindset – do you have it?\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/entrepreneur-mindset-do-you-have-it.htm\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/entrepreneur-mindset-do-you-have-it.htm#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 13 Sep 2013 15:43:35 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/?p=18816\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:608:\"<p>Let’s face it: being an entrepreneur is tough.&#160; It easy to get discouraged when you are “chief cook and bottle-washer” of your business, which most of us are.&#160; You have to manage every aspect from service delivery, to marketing, to infrastructure and accounting, in addition to (often enough) nerve-wracking income fluctuations. For all these reasons, [&#8230;]</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/entrepreneur-mindset-do-you-have-it.htm\">Entrepreneur mindset &#8211; do you have it?</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com\">WordPress Training</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"marc\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3376:\"<p></p><p>Let’s face it: being an entrepreneur is tough.&#160; It easy to get discouraged when you are “chief cook and bottle-washer” of your business, which most of us are.&#160; You have to manage every aspect from service delivery, to marketing, to infrastructure and accounting, in addition to (often enough) nerve-wracking income fluctuations.</p>  <p>For all these reasons, “mindset” (or “attitude”) is key.&#160; Quite simply it will make the difference between success and failure – not to mention retaining your sanity.&#160; And we solo-preneurs in particular need a double (triple) dose of this.&#160; We need to focus, be kind to ourselves, and seek support.&#160; And we need strategies that get results, both for changing our mindset and making business happen.</p>  <p>Well, nobody does this “mindset” thing better than my mentor and partner Christine Kane.&#160; I am actually such a fan that I wrote a complete review of her “Uplevel Your Business” program on my entrepreneur blog (you can find it <a href=\"http://lifestyledesignschool.com/2013/06/christine-kane-review-uplevel-your-business-2013-report/\">here</a>), which is, IMHO (in my humble opinion) the best entrepreneur training to be had for any money, particularly for service-type businesses.&#160; </p>  <p>But that’s another topic – what I want to say is that this coming <u>Wednesday Sept. 18, at 8pm EST</u>, Christine is presenting a special webinar on Mindset.&#160; Sign-up here for the free, live webinar, and/or to get the recording: </p>  <p><a href=\"https://christinekane.infusionsoft.com/go/mindsetmaster/marc\"><strong>&gt;&gt;&gt; Register Here for the Mindset Master Class &lt;&lt;&lt;</strong></a></p>  <p>To find out more, read Christine’s description of the event:</p>  <p>________________</p>  <p> It doesn&#8217;t really matter WHAT you want to create in your life &#8211; to build your business, thrive in corporate, live your dream&#8230;</p>  <p>&#8230;it&#8217;s all about your mindset.</p>  <p>The thing is, I see lots of people playing games trying to &quot;fix&quot; their mindset. Little tricks, tactics and tweaks&#8230;</p>  <p>&#8230;and of course, they always end up disappointed.</p>  <p>Well, I just posted a brand-new video for you about mindset. And most important, how you can create what you want by mastering the key steps of mindset.</p>  <p>Over two thousand people have learned this stuff from me&#8230; and now it&#8217;s 100% free for you to check out&#8230;and I guarantee it&#8217;ll change the way you think, live, and get wealthy.</p>  <p>(Yes, I know. That&#8217;s a lofty promise. But at this point, I think I&#8217;ve earned the right to say that.)</p>  <p><a href=\"https://christinekane.infusionsoft.com/go/mindsetmaster/marc\"><strong>Mindset Master Class &lt;&#8212; CLICK HERE</strong></a></p>  <p>Oh yeah. And wait til I give you the actual Manifestation Model once you&#8217;re in the training. You are going to LOVE it. It&#8217;s like a treasure map!</p>  <p>_______________</p>  <p>I will be on the call – hope to see you there!</p>  <p>To Your Success,</p>  <p>Marc&#160; Beneteau</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/entrepreneur-mindset-do-you-have-it.htm\">Entrepreneur mindset &#8211; do you have it?</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com\">WordPress Training</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/entrepreneur-mindset-do-you-have-it.htm/feed\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:44:\"Last few days to get WP Encyclopedia for $35\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/last-few-days-to-get-wp-encyclopedia-for-35.htm\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:85:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/last-few-days-to-get-wp-encyclopedia-for-35.htm#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 11 Sep 2013 14:58:32 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/?p=18807\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:566:\"<p>The WP Encyclopedia crowd funding campaign is ending this coming Sunday Sept 15.&#160; On Monday, the price goes up to retail ($147). The current offer on WP Encyclopedia is quite simply the best offer we have ever made – not to mention the best deal on WordPress and Web Marketing training for entrepreneurs on the [&#8230;]</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/last-few-days-to-get-wp-encyclopedia-for-35.htm\">Last few days to get WP Encyclopedia for $35</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com\">WordPress Training</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"marc\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3511:\"<p></p><p><strong><em>The WP Encyclopedia crowd funding campaign is ending this coming Sunday Sept 15.&#160; On Monday, the price goes up to retail ($147).</em></strong></p>  <p>The current offer on WP Encyclopedia is quite simply the best offer we have ever made – not to mention the best deal on WordPress and Web Marketing training for entrepreneurs on the web.&#160; Here is why: </p>  <ul>   <li>Immediate registration to our three, extremely popular Udemy short courses: <a href=\"https://www.udemy.com/wordpress-essentials/\">WordPress Essentials for Business</a>, <a href=\"https://www.udemy.com/wordpress-theme-selection/\">WordPress Theme Selection</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.udemy.com/wordpress-backup/\">WordPress Backup and Security</a>) – over 1500 people have taken these courses, leaving 45+ five-star reviews.&#160; Combined, these courses would cost you $76 alone.</li>    <li>The complete recordings of the <a href=\"http://www.wpacademy.com/wordpress-training/\">WordPress for Business Course</a>, covering ecommerce and payment systems, membership, SEO, online video production and distribution, and more ($99 value).</li>    <li>Access to the 2013 edition of WP Encyclopedia when it gets published in December.&#160; This is a greatly expanded version covering more themes, plugin review by category, case studies, WordPress Virtual Summit recordings, and more</li>    <li>The standalone DVD (2013 Edition) will be shipped to you in late December – imagine 300+ HD training videos on your computer and accessible without an internet connection</li>    <li>WP Encyclopedia is fully searchable – forget about learning web marketing from Youtube and Google.&#160; All of our videos are professionally produced, no-fluff, designed for busy entrepreneurs</li> </ul>  <p>What’s more, by supporting our crowd funding you are helping out thousands (maybe millions) of entrepreneurs worldwide by helping us create the most comprehensive, best-produced and most up-to-date “WordPress for business” resource on the planet.</p>  <p><strong><em>Here is the link:</em></strong></p>  <p><a title=\"http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/wordpress-business-encyclopedia-2013/x/3688052\" href=\"http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/wordpress-business-encyclopedia-2013/x/3688052\">http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/wordpress-business-encyclopedia-2013/x/3688052</a></p>  <p><strong><em>Remember that page comes down on Sunday night.</em></strong></p>  <h2>It’s not too late to join our September WP Live program (live training)</h2>  <p>The September WP Live course started yesterday, but the recording is available.&#160; Fast-track your learning curve and avoid time-sucks and lost opportunities by giving yourself the help you want from the get-go.&#160; Hundreds of people have attended our live courses – check out some of the video reviews <a href=\"http://www.wpacademy.com/wordpress-training/\">here</a>.&#160; </p>  <p>To purchase WP Live, follow the crowd-funding link above and make a donation of $300 or more.&#160; Then write to our <a href=\"mailto:support@wpacademy.com\">support@wpacademy.com</a> and tell them which monthly course (within the next year) you want to join.&#160; Simple.</p>  <p>Any questions or feedback, feel free to respond to this mail.</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/last-few-days-to-get-wp-encyclopedia-for-35.htm\">Last few days to get WP Encyclopedia for $35</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com\">WordPress Training</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:81:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/last-few-days-to-get-wp-encyclopedia-for-35.htm/feed\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"Free “WordPress Mechanic” live coaching sessions this week\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:89:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-wordpress-mechanic-live-coaching-sessions-this-week.htm\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:98:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-wordpress-mechanic-live-coaching-sessions-this-week.htm#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 09 Sep 2013 12:17:21 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/?p=18797\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:616:\"<p>Our next WordPress for Business (WP Live) course begins tomorrow, Tuesday Sept 10 at 2pm EST, and we are opening up three coaching sessions this week to the public!&#160; These are intended for people who are potentially interested in the full course to see how we work.&#160; However, there are no restrictions – just show-up [&#8230;]</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-wordpress-mechanic-live-coaching-sessions-this-week.htm\">Free &ldquo;WordPress Mechanic&rdquo; live coaching sessions this week</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com\">WordPress Training</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"marc\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3117:\"<p></p><p>Our next <a href=\"http://www.wpacademy.com/wordpress-training/\">WordPress for Business (WP Live)</a> course begins tomorrow, Tuesday Sept 10 at 2pm EST, and <strong><em>we are opening up three coaching sessions this week to the public</em></strong>!&#160; These are intended for people who are potentially interested in the full course to see how we work.&#160; However, there are no restrictions – just show-up with your site and your questions and let us see what we can do for you.&#160; </p>  <p>Here is the open (free) coaching schedule this week: </p>  <ul>   <li>Monday 9/9, 7-8pm EST (Marc)</li>    <li>Tuesday 9/10, 7-8pm EST (George)</li>    <li>Thursday 9/12, 2-3pm EST (Pamela)</li> </ul>  <p>Attend any session using this link:</p>  <p><a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/public\">http://members.wpacademy.com/public</a></p>  <p>No need to pre-register – just follow that link and join the meeting!&#160; Attendance is limited to 25 people and will likely fill-up, so come early.&#160; </p>  <p>(Note: we use the more powerful GotoMeeting technology for these groups, which allows public chats and two-way VOIP.&#160; Check it out, but if you come at the wrong time, nobody will be there)</p>  <h2>More about our live course (that begins tomorrow)</h2>  <p><strong><em>Our 8-week course “WP Live” gives you all of the training, all of the tools, and all of the support that you need to start creating professional WordPress websites</em></strong>.&#160; This is truly a unique program that you will not find anywhere else on the internet (and particularly at this price point).&#160; Read all about it <a href=\"http://www.wpacademy.com/wordpress-training/\">here</a>, and when you are ready to join, save yourself $50 by registering at the crowd-funding site with a donation of $300 or more: </p>  <p><a title=\"http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/wordpress-business-encyclopedia-2013/x/3688052\" href=\"http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/wordpress-business-encyclopedia-2013/x/3688052\">http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/wordpress-business-encyclopedia-2013/x/3688052</a></p>  <p>Note that the crowd-funding site (and the $50 discount) expires this coming Sunday night 9/15.&#160; You can even register for the live course this week, and then choose any WP Live session in the next year and write to our support&#160; – we will save your spot for you.&#160; </p>  <p>Best regards,</p>  <p><img title=\"marc-george-pamela\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px\" border=\"0\" alt=\"marc-george-pamela\" src=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/marc-george-pamela.jpg\" width=\"504\" height=\"154\" /></p>  <p>Your “WordPress Mechanics” – Marc, George and Pamela</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-wordpress-mechanic-live-coaching-sessions-this-week.htm\">Free &ldquo;WordPress Mechanic&rdquo; live coaching sessions this week</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com\">WordPress Training</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:94:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-wordpress-mechanic-live-coaching-sessions-this-week.htm/feed\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"Free Kindle Book + Webinar Recording\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:84:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-kindle-book-webinar-recording-open-immediately.htm\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:93:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-kindle-book-webinar-recording-open-immediately.htm#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 06 Sep 2013 15:41:48 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/?p=18782\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:704:\"<p>Webinar recording is published The recording of “KIndle Publishing and WordPress Tips for Beginners”, with George Plumley and Marc Beneteau has been published!&#160; See: http://members.wpacademy.com/w0-kindle Get George’s new ebook “100 Beginner WordPress Tips” for free on Amazon… … but only today (Friday 9/6).&#160; Here is the link: http://www.amazon.com/100-Beginner-WordPress-Tips-ebook/dp/B00EO26LTE/ You will want to grab that today [&#8230;]</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-kindle-book-webinar-recording-open-immediately.htm\">Free Kindle Book + Webinar Recording</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com\">WordPress Training</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"marc\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2099:\"<p></p><h3>Webinar recording is published</h3>  <p>The recording of “KIndle Publishing and WordPress Tips for Beginners”, with George Plumley and Marc Beneteau has been published!&#160; See:</p>  <p><a title=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/w0-kindle\" href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/w0-kindle\">http://members.wpacademy.com/w0-kindle</a></p>  <h3>Get George’s new ebook “100 Beginner WordPress Tips” for free on Amazon…</h3>  <p>… <strong><em>but only today (Friday 9/6).</em></strong>&#160; Here is the link:</p>  <p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/100-Beginner-WordPress-Tips-ebook/dp/B00EO26LTE/\">http://www.amazon.com/100-Beginner-WordPress-Tips-ebook/dp/B00EO26LTE/</a></p>  <p>You will want to grab that today – we can only make it free for one day on the Kindle store.</p>  <h3>New FREE WP Live demo coaching &amp; information session Monday!</h3>  <p>With our next course starting Tuesday Sept. 10 at 2pm, EST, I am running a <strong><em>live coaching demo and WP Live information session on Monday Sept 10, 2pm EST</em></strong>.</p>  <p>This is a live coaching (interactive) session using the more powerful GotoMeeting technology (as opposed to GotoWebinar which does not allow group chats).&#160; Please drop-in and see how we work!&#160; Attendees are invited to bring their questions, websites and problems and have me or George work on their sites with them.</p>  <p>We can only take 25 attendees!&#160; If the meeting maxes out, try again later in the hour.&#160; Use this link:</p>  <p><a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/public\">http://members.wpacademy.com/public</a></p>  <p>That meeting link is only good on Monday Sept 9, 2-3pm EST.&#160; If you try it any other time, there will be nobody there!</p>  <p>If you have any questions or feedback about upcoming course or WP Academy products or services, just reply to this mail.</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-kindle-book-webinar-recording-open-immediately.htm\">Free Kindle Book + Webinar Recording</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com\">WordPress Training</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:89:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-kindle-book-webinar-recording-open-immediately.htm/feed\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:35:\"WP Encyclopedia needs your support!\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/wp-encyclopedia-needs-your-support.htm\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/wp-encyclopedia-needs-your-support.htm#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 03 Sep 2013 15:14:19 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/?p=18767\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:540:\"<p>(Quick note to begin – over 400 people registered for today’s webinar Kindle Publishing &#38; WordPress Tips.&#160; Obviously this is a hot topic!&#160; It starts in a few hours, please join us if you can – and if you can’t join live, register anyway to get the recording and free eBook) We are in the [&#8230;]</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/wp-encyclopedia-needs-your-support.htm\">WP Encyclopedia needs your support!</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com\">WordPress Training</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"marc\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3610:\"<p></p><p>(Quick note to begin – over 400 people registered for today’s webinar <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-webinar-kindle-publishing-wordpress-tips.htm\">Kindle Publishing &amp; WordPress Tips</a>.&#160; Obviously this is a hot topic!&#160; It starts in a few hours, please join us if you can – and if you can’t join live, register anyway to get the recording and free eBook)</p>  <p><strong><em>We are in the final two weeks of crowd-funding the next edition of the </em></strong><a href=\"http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/wordpress-business-encyclopedia-2013\"><strong><em>WordPress Business Encyclopedia</em></strong></a>.&#160;&#160; We have already reached 30% of the $10,000 funding goal (and this despite the fact I have barely been at the computer most of August, as I have moved myself and a large household to North Carolina!).&#160; But much more is needed and I would like to explain why.</p>  <p>WP Encyclopedia 2013 is designed as a major expansion and rewrite of our popular live course, the <a href=\"http://www.wpacademy.com/wordpress-training/\">WordPress for Business Course</a>.&#160; Now the live course, which includes support, themes, stock photos and more, is already an amazing value (you can register in our upcoming course that starts Sept 10 with a contribution of $300 or more). But with a donation of just $35 in the next few weeks, you can access ALL of our current training resources AND get WP Encyclopedia 2013 when it comes out in December. </p>  <p>WP Encyclopedia 2013 is designed for the “do it yourself”, self-starter type of person who needs general guidance and/or specific tutorials on creating a business-oriented website. It will save you many hours of research by giving you best practices and best resources.&#160; It will also include (for the first time on the web) review articles and fast-start videos of all the best WordPress plugins by category.&#160; Have you ever spent hours researching the best plugin for a particular task (and then spent additional hours trying to configure it using documentation that was written by and for developers?)&#160; Well that time will soon be over.</p>  <p>I could go on and on, but let me just say – WP Encyclopedia 2013 is going to be a game-changer for anyone, at any level, engaged in creating WordPress websites.&#160; Reaching the $10k funding goal is important because it will allow me to focus exclusively on this for the next 3-4 months.&#160; I have already (very exciting news!) arranged with George to teach the fall course lineup.&#160; With this in place, I can research, write and shoot videos full-time for the rest of the year.&#160; </p>  <p>Please watch the intro video below, and then donate generously to this important project:</p>  <p><a href=\"http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/wordpress-business-encyclopedia-2013\"><img title=\"image\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px\" border=\"0\" alt=\"image\" src=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/image.png\" width=\"383\" height=\"288\" /></a></p>  <p>&#160;</p>  <p>Thank you for your support.&#160; Remember that the $35 price is only good until September 15, after which crowd funding ends and price reverts to $50. </p>  <p>To Your Success,</p>  <p>Marc</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/wp-encyclopedia-needs-your-support.htm\">WP Encyclopedia needs your support!</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com\">WordPress Training</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/wp-encyclopedia-needs-your-support.htm/feed\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"Free Webinar: Kindle Publishing &amp; WordPress Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-webinar-kindle-publishing-wordpress-tips.htm\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:87:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-webinar-kindle-publishing-wordpress-tips.htm#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 30 Aug 2013 14:59:53 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/?p=18762\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:576:\"<p>I have a real treat for you next week.&#160; Our very own George Plumley (WP Academy lead instructor and WordPress author) will be sharing the story of his first Kindle book called “100 Beginner WordPress Tips”.&#160; What’s more, he will be giving out a free copy of the book ($5 value) to anyone who registers [&#8230;]</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-webinar-kindle-publishing-wordpress-tips.htm\">Free Webinar: Kindle Publishing &amp; WordPress Tips</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com\">WordPress Training</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4:\"marc\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2825:\"<p></p><p><a href=\"http://seehowtips.com/\"><img style=\"float: right; display: inline\" alt=\"http://seehowtips.com/images/wordpress-tips-for-beginners.jpg\" align=\"right\" src=\"http://seehowtips.com/images/wordpress-tips-for-beginners.jpg\" width=\"177\" height=\"283\" /></a>I have a real treat for you next week.&#160; Our very own George Plumley (WP Academy lead instructor and WordPress author) will be sharing the story of his first Kindle book called “100 Beginner WordPress Tips”.&#160; What’s more, he will be giving out a free copy of the book ($5 value) to anyone who registers for the webinar!</p>  <h3>Free Webinar: Kindle Publishing and WordPress Tips, with George Plumley</h3>  <p><strong>Tuesday, Sept. 3, 2-3pm EST</strong></p>  <p><strong>Register here:</strong></p>  <p><a title=\"https://www3.gotomeeting.com/register/281704230\" href=\"https://www3.gotomeeting.com/register/281704230\"><strong>https://www3.gotomeeting.com/register/281704230</strong></a></p>  <p>(If you are not able to attend in person, register anyway to receive the recording)</p>  <p>George will talk for about 20 minutes about the dramatic changes in publishing brought on by Kindle and similar services and then spend about 20 minutes on his best WordPress tips for beginners.&#160; </p>  <p>Then I will take over and present: </p>  <h3>WP Academy Fall Course Schedule!</h3>  <p>We have finalized the fall WP Live course schedule (our famous WordPress for Business Course), as follows: </p>  <ul>   <li>Session 1: Tuesdays Sept 10 – Oct. 1, 2-4pm EST </li>    <li>Session 2: Tuesdays Oct. 8 – Oct. 29, 2-4pm EST </li>    <li>Session 3: Tuesdays Nov. 5 – Nov. 26, 2-4pm EST</li> </ul>  <p>This is the web’s premier WordPress &amp; Web Marketing Technology Training program for self-employed and small business.&#160; We are currently taking registrations (at a $50 discount!) through our ongoing crowd funding campaign here: </p>  <p><a href=\"http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/wordpress-business-encyclopedia-2013\"><strong>http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/wordpress-business-encyclopedia-2013</strong></a></p>  <p>Any donation at the $300 level or above includes access to any live course in the next year.&#160; This money will be used to fund development of the next generation of our revolutionary training system, the <a href=\"http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/wordpress-business-encyclopedia-2013\">WordPress Business Encyclopedia</a>.</p>  <p>I look forward to a great learning experience with y’all on Tuesday’s webinar – and a special welcome to our Fall WP Live students.</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-webinar-kindle-publishing-wordpress-tips.htm\">Free Webinar: Kindle Publishing &amp; WordPress Tips</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://members.wpacademy.com\">WordPress Training</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/free-webinar-kindle-publishing-wordpress-tips.htm/feed\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:47:\"http://members.wpacademy.com/category/news/feed\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"hourly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";